# Contact — Points Harvest

Questions, bug reports, feature ideas — all welcome. For bugs and feature requests, open a GitHub issue: {{ site.githubUrl }}/issues. For everything else, email is the fastest way to reach us.

## Channels

- **Email** — pointsharvest@protonmail.com
- **GitHub Issues** — {{ site.githubUrl }}/issues

## Topics

- **Bug reports** — Prefer GitHub issues for bugs. Include your browser version, what you were doing, and anything the extension logged in the debug panel.
- **Feature requests** — Tell us what you want it to do and the problem you're trying to solve. Concrete examples help a lot.
- **General feedback** — Love it, hate it, or have a question? We read every message and appreciate the input.
